OL,3,CMany foundation year students 'not
OL,4,Cgetting degree they were promised'
OL,6,FMany foundation year courses are "not
OL,7,Fdoing justice to students" who are
OL,8,Ffailing to get the degree they were
OL,9,Fpromised, a think tank has suggested.
OL,11,FFoundation years ` which are one-year
OL,12,Fcourses designed to prepare students
OL,13,Ffor degree-level study ` have "grown
OL,14,Fexplosively" over the past decade, a
OL,15,Freport by the Higher Education Policy
OL,16,FInstitute (Hepi) think tank has found.
