OL,3,CMany foundation year students 'not
OL,4,Cgetting degree they were promised'
OL,6,FMore than 69,000 UK-domiciled students
OL,7,Fentered foundation years at higher
OL,8,Feducation institutions in England in
OL,9,F2021/22, compared to nearly 8,500 in
OL,10,F2011/12, Government figures suggest.
OL,12,FStudents who pass their foundation
OL,13,Fyear do not usually receive a
OL,14,Fstandalone qualification, but instead
OL,15,Fprogress to degree courses.
OL,17,FBut the Hepi report suggested that 74%
OL,18,Fof students continued in higher
OL,19,Feducation after completing their
OL,20,Ffoundation year.
