OL,3,CMany foundation year students 'not
OL,4,Cgetting degree they were promised'
OL,6,FThis was lower than the 91% of full-
OL,7,Ftime undergraduates who continued in
OL,8,Fhigher education after their first
OL,9,Fyear, according to the think tank.
OL,11,FThere are reports that institutions
OL,12,Fmay be using foundation years to
OL,13,F"inflate their tariff scores
OL,14,Fartificially" which is "clearly of
OL,15,Fconcern", the paper said.
OL,17,FBut it added there was "no clear
OL,18,Fevidence" that students were being
OL,19,Fencouraged to take foundation years.
