OL,6,FThe think tank is calling on the
OL,7,FOffice for Students (OfS) to withdraw
OL,8,Fstudent finance from foundation year
OL,9,Fcourses which deliver poor outcomes
OL,10,Ffor students.
OL,12,FUniversities should not run foundation
OL,13,Fcourses "unless they can be confident
OL,14,Fthey can properly support every single
OL,15,Fstudent", the author of the report
OL,16,Fsaid.
