OL,4,Cgetting degree they were promised'
OL,6,FIn July, the Prime Minister announced
OL,7,Fthat the maximum fee that universities
OL,8,Fcould charge for some classroom-based
OL,9,Ffoundation year courses, such as
OL,10,Fbusiness and social sciences, would be
OL,11,Freduced to #5,760.
OL,13,FBut the think tank report has called
OL,14,Ffor the Government to abandon the fee
OL,15,Freduction ` which is due to come into
OL,16,Feffect in 2025/26 ` as it warned that
OL,17,Fmany of the affected courses may no
OL,18,Flonger be financially viable and the
OL,19,Fpolicy could "make the quality of some
OL,20,Fcourses worse".
