OL,6,F"Ironically, the only classroom-based
OL,7,Fcategory not necessarily loss-making
OL,8,Fwill be business courses ` the courses
OL,9,Fnamed by the Department for Education
OL,10,F(DfE) as being the target of the
OL,11,Fclampdown," the report said.
OL,13,FLast month, Universities UK (UUK) said
OL,14,Fit would review international student
OL,15,Fadmissions processes following the
OL,16,Fallegations of "bad practice" by
OL,17,Fagents recruiting overseas students
OL,18,Ffor UK universities.
