OL,6,FIt came after a Sunday Times
OL,7,Finvestigation included claims by
OL,8,Frecruitment agents who allegedly said
OL,9,Ffoundation year courses with lower
OL,10,Fgrade requirements provided overseas
OL,11,Fstudents with easier access to degree
OL,12,Fcourses at UK universities.
OL,14,FThe Hepi report has estimated that
OL,15,Faround 14% of students on integrated
OL,16,Ffoundation years were international
OL,17,Fstudents in 2020/21.
