OL,6,FAmong the overseas students on
OL,7,Fintegrated foundation years, some 71%
OL,8,Fcontinued in higher education,
OL,9,Fcompared to three-quarters (75%) of
OL,10,Fdomestic students, according to the
OL,11,Fpaper.
OL,13,FThese findings relate only to
OL,14,Fintegrated foundation years ` which
OL,15,Fare part of a full-time undergraduate
OL,16,Fdegree programme.
