OL,6,FJosh Freeman, policy manager at Hepi
OL,7,Fand author of the report, said: "In
OL,8,Fthe blink of an eye, and without
OL,9,Fproper scrutiny, foundation year
OL,10,Fcourses have become extraordinarily
OL,11,Fpopular.
OL,13,F"Many of these courses are excellent,
OL,14,Fgiving opportunities to students with
OL,15,Fincredible potential but need more
OL,16,Fsupport to succeed in higher education.
