OL,4,Cgetting degree they were promised'
OL,6,F"But many others are not doing justice
OL,7,Fto students, who, despite giving
OL,8,Fsignificant money, time and energy,
OL,9,Fare not getting the degree they were
OL,10,Fpromised."
OL,12,FHe added: "The Government also bears
OL,13,Fsome responsibility. Its policy of
OL,14,Fslashing fees for business and
OL,15,Fhumanities courses is simplistic and
OL,16,Fmight make quality worse.
