OL,6,F"Other courses, including Stem
OL,7,F(science, technology, engineering and
OL,8,Fmathematics) courses, are at serious
OL,9,Frisk of being financially unviable
OL,10,Fbecause universities are limited in
OL,11,Fwhat they can charge.
OL,13,F"It's time for everyone to wake up.
OL,14,FUniversities shouldn't be running
OL,15,Fthese courses unless they can be
OL,16,Fconfident they can properly support
OL,17,Fevery single student.
