OL,6,F"And the Office for Students should
OL,7,Fmake a serious attempt to distinguish
OL,8,Fexcellent foundation year courses from
OL,9,Fthose which fail to meet quality
OL,10,Fstandards."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for UUK said:
OL,13,F"Foundation years play an incredibly
OL,14,Fimportant role in supporting access to
OL,15,Fhigher education for those who would
OL,16,Fotherwise be unable to attend. Many
OL,17,Fstudents who enrol on these courses
OL,18,Fare mature students or students from
OL,19,Fdisadvantaged backgrounds.
