OL,6,F"These courses are fantastic
OL,7,Fopportunities for learners and enable
OL,8,Fthem to develop their skills before
OL,9,Fentering a full degree programme.
OL,10,FHowever, it is right that the Office
OL,11,Ffor Students acts as a backstop in any
OL,12,Fcase where the quality of a programme
OL,13,Fdoes not meet regulatory standards.
OL,15,F"To ensure the sector's ongoing
OL,16,Fsustainability it is important that
OL,17,Fhigher education is appropriately
OL,18,Ffunded. The decision to reduce the
OL,19,Ffunding for certain foundation year
OL,20,Fcourses will only make this worse."
